<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.3.9">
<l>uraikka vallē ṉallēṉu ṉulappil kīrtti veḷḷattiṉ</l>
<l>karaikka ṇeṉṟu celvaṉāṉ kātaṉ maiya lēṟiṉēṉ</l>
<l>puraippi lāta paramparaṉē poyyi lāta parañcuṭarē</l>
<l>iraittu nalla mēṉmakka ḷētta yāṉu mēttiṉēṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I cannot speak. When shall I go to the shore of the flood</l>
<l>of your unending fame? I rose in the intoxication of love.</l>
<l>O Highest of the high with equal, o highest light without false,</l>
<l>while former people cried out [and] praised [your] good [qualities], I too praise.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
